QIWI_PLUGIN_DESCRIPTION: Powercord plugin that allows you to manipulate with your QIWI Wallet account.
QIWI_PLUGIN_SETTINGS_OAUTH_DESC: Qiwi OAuth token is used to obtain QIWI account information.
QIWI_PLUGIN_SETTINGS_PERSON_ID_DESC: In other words, the phone number that was used to create the Qiwi wallet.
